  • Enum Constant Summary

    Enum Constants
    Enum Constant
    Description
    APPEND
    Appends the resources in the source file to the existing resources of the specified type, without modifying any existing resources.
    ERROR_IF_EXISTS
    If the resource type already exists, an error is raised.
    IGNORE
    Ignores the resources in the source file if the resource type already exists, otherwise adds the resources in the source file.
    MERGE
    Matches existing resources with updated resources in the source file based on their ID, and either update the existing resources or add new resources as appropriate.
    OVERWRITE
    Results in all existing resources of the specified type to be deleted and replaced with the contents of the source file.
